processes.abstract: Transforms a file input into JSON file containing an array of file references as value.

processes.title: JSON array to NetCDF
processes.abstract: Extracts and fetches NetCDF files from a JSON file containing an URL string array, and provides them on the output directory.

processes.title: Metalink to NetCDF
processes.abstract: Extracts and fetches NetCDF files from a Metalink file containing an URL, and outputs the NetCDF file at a given. Index of the list.
